# Setting Up User Groups

Before deploying to non-user targets ({{- if eq .include_dev_environment "yes" }}dev, {{- end }}stage{{- if eq .environment_setup "full" }}, prod{{- end }}), you must create the required groups in your Databricks workspace. The `user` target works immediately with no group dependencies.

These are custom groups you create, not system groups.

