## Required Groups by Environment

{{- if eq .environment_setup "full" }}
Your bundle is configured with **full environment setup** (user{{- if eq .include_dev_environment "yes" }}, dev{{- end }}, stage, prod), requiring {{- if eq .include_dev_environment "yes" }} 4 {{- else }} 4 {{- end }} groups.
{{- else }}
Your bundle is configured with **minimal environment setup** (user, stage), requiring 3 groups.
{{- end }}

### 1. developers (Required for {{- if eq .include_dev_environment "yes" }} dev,{{- end }} stage)
- **Purpose**: Data engineers and developers working on data pipelines
- **Access**:
{{- if eq .include_dev_environment "yes" }}
  - **dev**: Full access (ALL_PRIVILEGES) to all schemas + CAN_MANAGE on resources
{{- end }}
  - **stage**: Read-only (USE_SCHEMA, SELECT) to all schemas + CAN_VIEW on resources
{{- if eq .environment_setup "full" }}
  - **prod**: Not granted direct access (automation via service principal)
{{- end }}

> **Note**: The `user` target uses your personal identity and does not reference any groups.

**Who to add**: Data engineers, ETL developers, data platform engineers

---

### 2. qa_team (Required for stage)
- **Purpose**: QA engineers testing data quality and pipelines
- **Access**:
  - **stage**: Read-only (USE_SCHEMA, SELECT) to all schemas
- **Who to add**: QA engineers, data quality analysts

---

{{- if eq .environment_setup "full" }}

### 3. operations_team (Required for prod)
- **Purpose**: Operations/SRE team for incident investigation and monitoring
- **Access**:
  - **prod**: Read-only (USE_SCHEMA, SELECT) to all schemas
- **Who to add**: SRE, DevOps, on-call engineers, platform team

---

### 4. analytics_team (Required for {{- if eq .include_dev_environment "yes" }}dev/{{- end }}stage/prod)
{{- else }}

### 3. analytics_team (Required for stage)
{{- end }}
- **Purpose**: Analytics and BI teams consuming curated data
- **Access**:
{{- if eq .include_dev_environment "yes" }}
  - **dev**: Read-only (USE_SCHEMA, SELECT) to all schemas (bronze, silver, gold)
{{- end }}
  - **stage**: Read-only (USE_SCHEMA, SELECT) to all schemas (bronze, silver, gold)
{{- if eq .environment_setup "full" }}
  - **prod**: Read-only (USE_SCHEMA, SELECT) to all schemas (bronze, silver, gold)
{{- end }}
- **Who to add**: Data analysts, BI developers, business users, data scientists

